languages.text: "Мои слова не ясны?.. Сожалею. Тяжело мыслить лишь половиной сознания. Некоторые понятия, данные и логические инструменты остались... в более нефункциональной половине меня".

"Are my words obscure? That is regrettable. Processing becomes difficult when you only have one half of your mind. Certain notions, data, and logical instruments were left... in the less functional part of me."

languages.text: “我的话很晦涩难懂吗？这真令人遗憾，当你只有一半意识的时候，处理问题会变得比较困难。一部分概念、数据和逻辑工具……被留在了我运转状态较差的那部分里。”
languages.original_text: "Are my words obscure? That is regrettable. Processing becomes difficult when you only have one half of your mind. Certain notions, data, and logical instruments were left... in the less functional part of me."

traits.locale_text: “我的话很晦涩难懂吗？这真令人遗憾，当你只有一半意识的时候，处理问题会变得比较困难。一部分概念、数据和逻辑工具……被留在了我运转状态较差的那部分里。”
traits.speaker: DoorLockerTechpriest1

languages.text: « Mes propos sont-ils obscurs ? C'est bien malheureux. Le traitement des informations se complique quand on n'a plus que la moitié de son esprit. Il y a des notions, des données et des instruments logiques qui sont restés... dans la partie la moins fonctionnelle de mon être. »
languages.original_text: "Are my words obscure? That is regrettable. Processing becomes difficult when you only have one half of your mind. Certain notions, data, and logical instruments were left... in the less functional part of me."

traits.speaker: DoorLockerTechpriest1

languages.text: 「私の言葉、わかりにくいかしら？残念だわ。頭が半分しかないから処理が難しいの。特定の観念や、データ、論理的な道具は…私の中の機能が失われた部分残されてしまった」
languages.original_text: "Are my words obscure? That is regrettable. Processing becomes difficult when you only have one half of your mind. Certain notions, data, and logical instruments were left... in the less functional part of me."

traits.locale_text: 「私の言葉、わかりにくいかしら？残念だわ。頭が半分しかないから処理が難しいの。特定の観念や、データ、論理的な道具は…私の中の機能が失われた部分残されてしまった」
traits.speaker: DoorLockerTechpriest1

languages.text: «¿Cuesta comprender mis palabras? Desafortunado, desde luego. Cuando solo se tiene la mitad de tu mente resulta difícil procesar información. Ciertas nociones, datos e instrumentos lógicos se han quedado... en mi parte menos funcional».
languages.original_text: "Are my words obscure? That is regrettable. Processing becomes difficult when you only have one half of your mind. Certain notions, data, and logical instruments were left... in the less functional part of me."

languages.text: "Sind meine Worte obskur? Das ist bedauerlich. Die Verarbeitung wird schwierig, wenn man nur einen halben Verstand zur Verfügung hat. Gewisse Konzepte, Daten und logische Instrumente blieben ... im weniger funktionellen Teil meiner selbst zurück."

languages.text: "Sözlerim çok mu müphem? Çok üzücü. İşleme, zihnin yalnızca tek yarısı çalıştığında oldukça zorlaşıyor. Belirli anlamlar, veriler ve mantıksal araçlar... İşlevselliği noksan olan kısmımda kaldı."
